  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0d9c \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbb \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d86\u0db4\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0d91\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who escaped the country after avoiding the proceedings is caught on his return",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Panadura Special Crime Investigation Unit says that a person who evaded the court and is returning to the island after fleeing to Dubai was arrested at the Katunayake International Airport during the proceedings regarding the fraud of more than 12 lakh rupees under the guise of providing foreign employment.",
        "The arrested person is a resident of Alubomulla, Panadura, the police said.",
        "Police said that since 2007, the suspect has defrauded people of different parts of the island on several occasions by saying that he would give them foreign jobs in European countries.",
        "The police said that while the charges against the suspect were being heard in the court, he said that he was a tourist for two months in the year 2019 and went to the state of Dubai and was engaged in a clandestine job there.",
        "An official who joined the raid said that the police, who observed information from the Immigration and Emigration Department, arrested the suspect with the help of the airport security officers based on information that he was coming to the island on the 26th.",
        "The suspect was supposed to be produced before the Panadura Magistrate's Court on the charge of avoiding the court."
      ],
